X.mat : The mail itself as a string 
y.mat : 1 for spam 0 for mail.

Algorithm proposition: Classification

X: features of email
y: 1 for spam, 0 for mail.


Dataset1
m = 5171 emails
y = 1499 spams (29%), 3672 mails (71%)

