Word choosing:
When looking at a bunch of spam email y = 1, with this piece of shell script

tr -c '[:alnum:]' '[\n*]' < spam.mat| sort | uniq -c | sort -nr | head  -10

this will prints out the frequencies of the word appearances descending order.
